Because exact stroke-to-image correspondence was not available, score-level fusion was performed on an index-aligned paired subset within each condition. Therefore, the fusion result should be interpreted as modality-level confirmation rather than exact cycle-level sensor fusion.
Force alone already separates new and wear perfectly.
Sheet PatchCore is the strongest image-only modality.
Punch PatchCore is useful but less reliable.
Image-only fusion of Punch + Sheet is almost perfect.
Adding images to force does not improve AUC because force is already perfect, but it adds visual confirmation and interpretability.
